<md>
#### Renaming (`-rename`)
Renames a file or folder in place.

**Syntax:** `MANAGE -rename [-dir] <old_name> as <new_name>`

```
<-@ Rename a file @->
<@|MANAGE -rename @ROOT/old_name.txt as @ROOT/new_name.txt
---end---

<-@ Rename a folder @->
<@|MANAGE -rename -dir @ROOT/docs as @ROOT/documentation
---end---
```

</md>